Using data & diagram from [r-causal: chapter 2](https://www.r-causal.org/chapters/02-whole-game#model-our-assumptions)


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(gtsummary)
library(corrr)
```
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
net_data <- read_rds(here("data/causal/net_data.Rds"))
```
:::


